---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Website Systems" description="A website that catches leads, follows up automatically, and tells you exactly where every job came from. That's Step 1." currentPage="websites">

    <!-- SECTION 1 — HERO -->
    <section class="section section--hero surface-base noise-bg">
        <div class="grid-page grid-align-center">
            <div class="col-left-7 stack-6">
                <p class="t-eyebrow">Step 1 — Build the Foundation</p>
                <h1 class="t-display t-display--hero">
                    YOUR WEBSITE<br />
                    SHOULD BOOK JOBS.<br />
                    <span style="color: var(--color-brand);">NOT JUST LOOK PRETTY.</span>
                </h1>
                <p class="t-body t-body--lg" style="max-width: 55ch;">
                    You already have a website. It looks fine. But it doesn't follow up on leads. It doesn't track where they came from. It doesn't text back missed calls. It doesn't request reviews.
                </p>
                <p class="t-body t-body--md" style="max-width: 55ch; color: var(--color-text-primary); font-weight: 500;">
                    It's a brochure. And brochures don't book jobs.
                </p>
                <a href="/contact" class="btn btn--primary btn--lg">Start Your System →</a>
            </div>
            <div class="col-right-5">
                <div style="aspect-ratio: 4/5; background: var(--color-surface-elevated); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">
                    <img src="/images/logos/badmouth-logo-stacked.png" alt="Badmouth Digital" style="width: 60%; opacity: 0.15;" />
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>


    <!-- SECTION 2 — PROBLEM -->
    <section class="section section--split section--padded surface-sunken">
        <div class="grid-page grid-align-center grid-gap-lg">
            <div class="col-left-7 stack-6">
                <p class="t-eyebrow">The Real Problem</p>
                <h2 class="t-display t-display--section">
                    GREAT WEBSITE.<br />
                    <span class="t-accent t-crt-shake">ZERO SYSTEM.</span>
                </h2>
                <p class="t-body t-body--md" style="max-width: 55ch;">
                    You're getting leads. Some of them, anyway. But here's what's happening to most of them:
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-right-5">
                <div class="card stack-3" style="border-left: 3px solid var(--color-brand);">
                    <p class="t-body t-body--sm">Phone rings on a job. Goes to voicemail. Nobody follows up.</p>
                    <p class="t-body t-body--sm">Form gets submitted. Sits in your inbox. Gets buried.</p>
                    <p class="t-body t-body--sm">Lead visits your site twice. You never know.</p>
                    <p class="t-body t-body--sm">Customer finishes a job. No review request goes out.</p>
                    <p class="t-body t-body--sm">You can't tell which ad, which page, which source brought in which job.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SECTION 3 — REFRAME -->
    <section class="section section--statement section--padded surface-base">
        <div class="grid-page">
            <div class="col-content stack-6 text-center">
                <p class="t-eyebrow">What You Actually Need</p>
                <h2 class="t-display t-display--section" style="margin-inline: auto;">
                    NOT JUST A WEBSITE.<br />
                    <span class="t-accent t-flicker">A SYSTEM THAT CATCHES AND CONVERTS.</span>
                </h2>
                <p class="t-body t-body--lg" style="margin-inline: auto; max-width: 60ch;">
                    A website system catches every lead that shows up, follows up automatically, tracks everything, and connects to the tools you're already using. It runs without you touching it.
                </p>
                <p class="t-body t-body--md" style="margin-inline: auto; max-width: 60ch; color: var(--color-text-primary); font-weight: 600;">
                    This is Step 1 for a reason. Nothing else works without it.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <hr class="section-divider" />

    <!-- SECTION 4 — WHAT'S INCLUDED -->
    <section class="section section--padded surface-elevated">
        <div class="grid-page grid-gap-lg">
            <div class="col-full text-center stack-6">
                <p class="t-eyebrow">What's Inside</p>
                <h2 class="t-display t-display--section" style="margin-inline: auto;">
                    WHAT YOUR <span class="t-accent t-flicker">WEBSITE SYSTEM</span> INCLUDES.
                </h2>
            </div>
            <div class="col-full">
                <div class="inner-grid-3">
                    <div class="card stack-3">
                        <h3 class="t-display t-display--card">LEAD CAPTURE</h3>
                        <p class="t-body t-body--sm">Forms, phone tracking, and CTAs built to convert — not just collect dust.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card stack-3">
                        <h3 class="t-display t-display--card">MISSED CALL TEXTBACK</h3>
                        <p class="t-body t-body--sm">Someone calls and you can't answer? They get a text. Automatically. Before they call your competitor.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card stack-3">
                        <h3 class="t-display t-display--card">CRM CONNECTION</h3>
                        <p class="t-body t-body--sm">Every lead lands in your CRM with source, page, and status. No spreadsheets. No guessing.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card stack-3">
                        <h3 class="t-display t-display--card">REVIEW AUTOMATION</h3>
                        <p class="t-body t-body--sm">After a job, your system requests reviews. On autopilot. So your Google profile stays fed.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card stack-3">
                        <h3 class="t-display t-display--card">GOOGLE PROFILE LINK</h3>
                        <p class="t-body t-body--sm">Your site connects to your Google Business Profile. Consistent info. Linked presence. Better rankings.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card stack-3">
                        <h3 class="t-display t-display--card">SOURCE TRACKING</h3>
                        <p class="t-body t-body--sm">Know where every lead came from. Which page. Which ad. Which source. No more guessing what works.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SECTION 5 — PACKAGES -->
    <section class="section section--padded surface-sunken">
        <div class="grid-page grid-gap-lg">
            <div class="col-full text-center stack-6">
                <p class="t-eyebrow">Packages</p>
                <h2 class="t-display t-display--section" style="margin-inline: auto;">
                    PICK YOUR <span class="t-accent t-flicker">STARTING POINT.</span>
                </h2>
            </div>
            <div class="col-full">
                <div class="inner-grid-3">
                    <!-- Foundation -->
                    <div class="card stack-4" style="border-top: 3px solid var(--color-brand);">
                        <p class="t-eyebrow" style="color: var(--color-text-muted);">Package 1</p>
                        <h3 class="t-display t-display--card">FOUNDATION</h3>
                        <p class="t-display t-display--subsection t-accent">$3,500</p>
                        <p class="t-body t-body--sm" style="color: var(--color-text-primary); font-weight: 600;">The essentials.</p>
                        <ul class="t-body t-body--sm" style="padding-left: 1.2em;">
                            <li>5-page website</li>
                            <li>Mobile-first design</li>
                            <li>Lead capture forms</li>
                            <li>Missed call text-back</li>
                            <li>Basic CRM setup</li>
                            <li>Google Business Profile link</li>
                            <li>Source tracking</li>
                        </ul>
                        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn--primary btn--sm" style="margin-top: auto;">Start Here →</a>
                    </div>
                    <!-- Growth -->
                    <div class="card stack-4" style="border-top: 3px solid var(--theme-accent-teal); position: relative;">
                        <span style="position: absolute; top: -12px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); background: var(--theme-accent-teal); color: var(--color-surface-base); font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.65rem; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.15em; padding: 4px 16px;">Most Popular</span>
                        <p class="t-eyebrow" style="color: var(--theme-accent-teal);">Package 2</p>
                        <h3 class="t-display t-display--card">GROWTH</h3>
                        <p class="t-display t-display--subsection" style="color: var(--theme-accent-teal);">$6,000</p>
                        <p class="t-body t-body--sm" style="color: var(--color-text-primary); font-weight: 600;">Everything in Foundation, plus:</p>
                        <ul class="t-body t-body--sm" style="padding-left: 1.2em;">
                            <li>Up to 10 pages</li>
                            <li>Service area pages</li>
                            <li>Advanced automations</li>
                            <li>Review request sequences</li>
                            <li>Follow-up email/text sequences</li>
                            <li>SEO-ready structure</li>
                            <li>Ad-ready landing pages</li>
                        </ul>
                        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn--primary btn--sm" style="margin-top: auto;">Get Growth →</a>
                    </div>
                    <!-- Custom -->
                    <div class="card stack-4" style="border-top: 3px solid var(--theme-accent-yellow);">
                        <p class="t-eyebrow" style="color: var(--theme-accent-yellow);">Package 3</p>
                        <h3 class="t-display t-display--card">CUSTOM BUILD</h3>
                        <p class="t-display t-display--subsection" style="color: var(--theme-accent-yellow);">Custom</p>
                        <p class="t-body t-body--sm" style="color: var(--color-text-primary); font-weight: 600;">For businesses that need more.</p>
                        <ul class="t-body t-body--sm" style="padding-left: 1.2em;">
                            <li>Unlimited pages</li>
                            <li>Multi-location support</li>
                            <li>Custom integrations</li>
                            <li>Advanced CRM workflows</li>
                            <li>Team dashboards</li>
                            <li>Priority support</li>
                        </ul>
                        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn--outline btn--sm" style="margin-top: auto;">Let's Talk →</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-full text-center">
                <p class="t-body t-body--sm" style="color: var(--color-text-muted); max-width: 55ch; margin-inline: auto;">
                    Every package includes the system. Not just a website. Not just a design. A website that catches leads, follows up, and tracks everything. That's what makes it Step 1.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SECTION 6 — WHAT HAPPENS NEXT -->
    <section class="section section--split section--padded surface-base">
        <div class="grid-page grid-align-center grid-gap-lg">
            <div class="col-left-7 stack-6">
                <p class="t-eyebrow">What Happens Next</p>
                <h2 class="t-display t-display--section">
                    HERE'S HOW <span class="t-accent t-flicker">IT WORKS.</span>
                </h2>
                <div class="stack-6">
                    <div class="stack-2" style="border-left: 3px solid var(--color-brand); padding-left: var(--space-4);">
                        <p class="t-eyebrow" style="color: var(--color-text-muted);">01</p>
                        <p class="t-body t-body--md" style="color: var(--color-text-primary); font-weight: 600;">You fill out the form.</p>
                        <p class="t-body t-body--sm">Tell us what's going on. We'll check your stuff before we talk.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stack-2" style="border-left: 3px solid var(--theme-accent-teal); padding-left: var(--space-4);">
                        <p class="t-eyebrow" style="color: var(--color-text-muted);">02</p>
                        <p class="t-body t-body--md" style="color: var(--color-text-primary); font-weight: 600;">We diagnose.</p>
                        <p class="t-body t-body--sm">We look at your site, tracking, follow-up, and lead flow. We come with answers.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stack-2" style="border-left: 3px solid var(--theme-accent-yellow); padding-left: var(--space-4);">
                        <p class="t-eyebrow" style="color: var(--color-text-muted);">03</p>
                        <p class="t-body t-body--md" style="color: var(--color-text-primary); font-weight: 600;">We build it.</p>
                        <p class="t-body t-body--sm">Your system gets built, connected, and tested. You approve before it goes live.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stack-2" style="border-left: 3px solid var(--color-brand); padding-left: var(--space-4);">
                        <p class="t-eyebrow" style="color: var(--color-text-muted);">04</p>
                        <p class="t-body t-body--md" style="color: var(--color-text-primary); font-weight: 600;">Launch + grow.</p>
                        <p class="t-body t-body--sm">Your system goes live. Everything works. Then we talk about Step 2.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-right-5">
                <div class="card stack-4" style="border-left: 3px solid var(--theme-accent-teal);">
                    <p class="t-body t-body--sm" style="color: var(--theme-accent-teal); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em;">Why Step 1 First?</p>
                    <p class="t-body t-body--sm">SEO sends people to your site. If it can't convert, they bounce.</p>
                    <p class="t-body t-body--sm">Ads drive traffic. If there's no follow-up, you lose them.</p>
                    <p class="t-body t-body--sm">Every dollar you spend on marketing lands on your website first. Make sure it's ready.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SECTION 7 — CTA -->
    <section class="section section--cta section--padded section--mic-drop has-scanlines" style="position: relative;">
        <div class="grid-page" style="position: relative; z-index: 2;">
            <div class="col-content text-center stack-4">
                <h2 class="t-display t-display--section" style="color: #fff; margin-inline: auto;">
                    READY TO BUILD A WEBSITE THAT<br />
                    <span class="mic-drop__headline">ACTUALLY BOOKS JOBS?</span>
                </h2>
                <p class="t-body t-body--lg" style="margin-inline: auto; max-width: 50ch; margin-top: var(--space-4);">
                    Fill out the form. We'll check your current setup and tell you exactly what's missing.
                </p>
                <a href="/contact" class="btn btn--lg">Diagnose Your System →</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SECTION 8 — REINFORCEMENT -->
    <section class="section section--statement section--padded-sm surface-pure">
        <div class="grid-page">
            <div class="col-content text-center">
                <p class="t-body t-body--lg" style="margin-inline: auto; max-width: 55ch; color: var(--color-text-primary); font-weight: 500;">
                    Step 1 isn't optional. It's where everything starts. Build the foundation first.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

</BaseLayout>
